.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Hobby: card-games, drawing, cooking, dancing, collecting
Transport: bike, bus, car, van, subway
Beverage: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
Cigar: card-gamesmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Game: poker, domino, scrabble, bridge, chess
1. Transport:bike == Hobby:cooking
2. Transport:swedish == Game:scrabble
3. Transport:bus == Beverage:tea
4. Hobby:drawing is on the left of Hobby:dancing
5. Hobby:drawing == Beverage:coffee
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Game:domino
7. Hobby:collecting == Cigar:dunhill
8. Beverage:milk is in the middle
9. Transport:van is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Game:poker
11. Game:chesss is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:card-gamesmaster == Beverage:beer
13. Transport:car == Cigar:prince
14. Transport:van is on the left or right of Hobby:card-games
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Beverage:water

